{
  "stem": "19923.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 63.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The train went as far as Villefranche, and we loaded up onto-- onto trucks that were given to us and we went to Seyre et Nailloux during the-- during the fighting.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "France had not yet been divided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germany was in the process of conquering France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As history will say, will attest to the fact that France was divided into the German occupied zone and the Vichy government by-- headed by Marshal Petain, who later turned out to be considered a traitor.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, southern France was occupied by the French but the police were puppets and they were-- they were actually doing the bidding of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, at that particular time also, when we landed there, there-- there was no place for us to stay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had 100 children and a few adults that were in charge of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had no food, we had no blankets, we had nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they gave us little granary that was in the village to use for-- for sleeping purposes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put straw on the floor, so we all slept on straw, called paille in French.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we lived there until finally, the Swiss Red Cross started sending supplies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they sent beds, cots, blankets, and whatever they could to assist the-- the people that were homeless there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That time was also the time when the French army were being demobilized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were all sent south after the Germans conquered France and they all were in, in villages, cities, and towns of southern France sitting around, waiting to be demobilize.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course, there was a lot of ill feeling toward the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
